divs: Sighting Detailsthis one was a strange looking craft this was last summer when i saw this one it was late a night and i was getting ready for bed when i looked out the window and noticed this strange spinner top looking object flying across the sky it was weird and it looked like it had electrical charges circling all around it this one is definitely hard to explain it was the strangest object that i have seen in the sky i don't know what this thing was this sighting lasted for probaby four minutes then i lost sight of the craft what was strange about this sighting was the electrical charges going around the craft it looked blue and pink it switched off and on between the two colors
Summary: strange spinner top ufo with electrical charges circling all around it
